sentences.english: We recorded 87 units in NR altogether.
sentences.chinese: 实验共记录了87个中缝核单位。

sentences.english: The midpalatal sutural expansion is a process of bone tissue regeneration and fibrous tissue repair.
sentences.chinese: 腭中缝改建的过程是纤维修复和骨组织再生过程。

sentences.english: In addition, in 5 of the 9 cases, a few labeled neurons were observed in the nucleus raphe dorsalis.
sentences.chinese: 另外，背中缝核在9例中只有5例出现少量标记细胞。

sentences.english: Nucleus raphe dorsalis (RD) plays an important role in acupuncture analgesia.
sentences.chinese: 中缝背核在针剌镇痛过程中起重要作用。

sentences.english: Median raphe nucleus did not show the decreased SERT labeling.
sentences.chinese: 中缝正中核SERT标记强度未见显著降低。

sentences.english: Objective To investigate the efferent pathway from the dorsal raphe nucleus to the inner ear.
sentences.chinese: 目的探讨中缝背核至内耳的传出神经通路。

sentences.english: The activation of NR units may play an important role ia laser analgesia.
sentences.chinese: 中缝核单位激活可能在激光镇痛作用中起重要作用。

sentences.english: The breadth of the rat palatal suture after each experiment phases was measured.
sentences.chinese: 测量每个实验步骤结束时腭中缝的宽度。

sentences.english: There were slight differences in arch perimeter and midpalatal suture separation.
sentences.chinese: 在牙弓的周长和腭中缝打开上略有差异。

sentences.english: The projection of NOS positive neurons to nucleus accumbens can be found in dorsal raphe nucleus.
sentences.chinese: 中缝背核内有NOS阳性神经元向伏隔核投射。

sentences.english: Objective To observe the role of nucleus raphe magnus(NRM) in analgesia produced by the activation of muscle spindle afferent.
sentences.chinese: 目的观察中缝大核在肌梭传入镇痛中的作用。
